<refentry id="bif.Regrets" xreflabel="Regrets">

<refmeta>
<indexterm>
<primary>Regrets</primary>
</indexterm>

<refentrytitle>Regrets</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>Regrets</refname>
<refpurpose>
Returns the gain from deviating to an action or strategy
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
Regrets[profile->MIXED] =: LIST(LIST(NUMBER)) 
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>Regrets</function> 
returns a nested list of the regrets generated for each strategy by
<parameter>profile</parameter>.  The (i,j)th entry is the regret for player
i, strategy j.
</para>
</refsect1>

</refentry>


